    <h3 class="mt3">Problem</h3>
    <p>Wine retailers and producers don‚Äôt give consumers the information and tools they need to make purchase decisions.</p>
    <h3>Hypotheses & Tests</h3>
    <p>By understanding how and why people buy wine, you can design better experiences for consumers with an end result of selling more wine to more people.</p>
    <p>I built three prototypes, each testing different hypotheses. The first was a POP and paper interaction, the second was built in InVision and Sketch, and the third was built in Unity3D for the Oculus Rift and HTC Vive headsets.</p>
